item.title: How to delete object perfectly in pimpscape
item.dc:creator: @system system
item.description:
@system wrote:

you have to use replaceobject.

Example.
just add this with your addglobalobject or w/e

ReplaceObject(objectX, objectY, -1, -1, 0);

where “objectX” where you put the objects X coords, same with “objectY” but its y coords.
and just leave the rest.
That will delete the object.

Good luck.
